      "text": "ひゃっ！？　え、こ、ここ、こ、琴乃ひゃん！？\nなんで急にハグなんて……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyaa!? Ko‚ Ko‚ Kotono-chan!?\nWhy are you hugging me all of a sudden…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0666668693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 11.8431295831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "う、海より、渚の方が綺麗だよ\n大好き、ジュテーム……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're more beautiful than the ocean‚ Nagisa.\nI love you. Je t'aime…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0333335359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening",
      "startTime": 21.2215424657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
