      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.452834364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌の企画のこと？\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』、だっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the magazine project?\n\"Miracle☆Idol Birthday!\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0333329002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4446257713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、やってみたかったことを叶えてくれる、お誕生日\n企画なんだけど……特にやりたいことが思いつかなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's a birthday project where you get to do something you've always wanted to do.\nBut I can't think of anything I really want to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2333329002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
